WEBVTT

00:00.063 --> 00:01.769
Previously on
<i>The Lying Game...</i>

00:01.770 --> 00:02.969
Someone broke into your house.

00:02.969 --> 00:03.969
My house?

00:04.003 --> 00:05.638
Yeah, and they stole
the laptop.

00:05.672 --> 00:07.840
Absolutely everything
is on that.

00:07.874 --> 00:09.809
So, I found your laptop
inside Ethan's Jeep.

00:09.843 --> 00:11.510
He's the one who stole it.

00:11.545 --> 00:12.938
That's crazy!

00:12.972 --> 00:14.964
I'm so sorry. I'm-I'm
all over the place.

00:14.998 --> 00:16.952
I like the Emma version.

00:16.986 --> 00:19.583
I do feel like I can trust you.

00:20.719 --> 00:22.885
- Welcome to Arroyo.
- Thrilled to be here.

00:22.919 --> 00:25.798
This really is my number.
I'll see ya.

00:25.832 --> 00:28.597
Our birth mother wanted Emma
back so badly

00:28.632 --> 00:30.570
that she faked her identity
to come get her.

00:30.604 --> 00:33.550
Do you want me to drive you back
to your motel now?

00:33.584 --> 00:34.917
Could I stay at your place?

00:35.922 --> 00:38.760
That's you, Emma,
and our mother.

01:07.957 --> 01:10.693
(crickets chirping)

01:11.596 --> 01:14.766
(car accelerates)

01:15.869 --> 01:17.639
(panting)

01:28.722 --> 01:30.824
(car door opens)

01:30.858 --> 01:34.961
Young lady, you've got
some explaining to do.

01:34.995 --> 01:36.963
Alec?

01:36.997 --> 01:38.764
We worked like hell
for three years

01:38.799 --> 01:40.999
to get that new state-of-the-art
facility at Arroyo,

01:41.034 --> 01:43.602
and this is where
you choose to run?

01:46.005 --> 01:48.673
All right.

01:48.707 --> 01:50.975
So... where you headed?

01:51.009 --> 01:52.610
(panting)

01:52.644 --> 01:55.014
I got turned around.

01:55.048 --> 01:56.882
Really?

01:56.917 --> 01:58.985
This is the same route I used
to drive you and Mads

01:59.019 --> 02:02.690
to Little Tykes Gymnastics
twice a week

02:02.724 --> 02:05.726
all through
elementary school.

02:05.760 --> 02:08.997
Things look different at night.

02:10.866 --> 02:13.803
Come on.

02:13.837 --> 02:15.805
I'll give you a ride home.

